The TTGO t-beam has no special onboard OLED pins
If an OLED is connected, it is done via i2C pins

Here are the pins used :
GPS_RX_PIN                  34
GPS_TX_PIN                  12

BUTTON_PIN                  38
BUTTON_PIN_MASK             GPIO_SEL_38

I2C_SDA                     21
I2C_SCL                     22
PMU_IRQ                     35

RADIO_SCLK_PIN               5
RADIO_MISO_PIN              19
RADIO_MOSI_PIN              27
RADIO_CS_PIN                18
RADIO_DIO0_PIN               26
RADIO_RST_PIN               23
RADIO_DIO1_PIN              33
RADIO_BUSY_PIN              32

BOARD_LED                   4
LED_ON                      LOW
LED_OFF                     HIGH

GPS_BAUD_RATE               9600
HAS_GPS
